OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FThe global climate is in a "state of
OL,7,Femergency," according to UN Secretary-
OL,8,FGeneral Antonio Guterres, as UN
OL,9,Fscientists warn that the world's
OL,10,Fclimate is more out of balance than at
OL,11,Fany time in observed history.
OL,13,FThe UN's weather and climate body has
OL,14,Freleased its annual state of the
OL,15,Fglobal climate report, warning that
OL,16,Fthe Earth has experienced rapid and
OL,17,Flarge-scale changes in recent decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
