FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774314171
OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FIntense heatwaves, heavy rainfall, and
OL,7,Fwildfires are among the many weather-
OL,8,Frelated causes of widespread deaths,
OL,9,Fdisruption, and devastation in 2025,
OL,10,Fimpacting millions of people and
OL,11,Fdriving vast economic losses,
OL,12,Faccording to the World Meteorological
OL,13,FOrganisation (WMO).
OL,15,F"Planet Earth is being pushed beyond
OL,16,Fits limits," Guterres said. "Every key
OL,17,Fclimate indicator is flashing red."
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@LO]xD@]OUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
