PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774314171
OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FIn the report, the WMO confirmed that
OL,7,F2015 to 2025 were the hottest 11 years
OL,8,Fon record, and last year was the
OL,9,Fsecond or third hottest year on
OL,10,Frecord, depending on the dataset.
OL,12,FThe global average temperature last
OL,13,Fyear was about 1.43 C above the 1850-
OL,14,F1990 pre-industrial average.
OL,16,FThis means the world is getting ever
OL,17,Fcloser to long-term average
OL,18,Ftemperatures breaching the key warming
OL,19,Fthreshold of 1.5 C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
