OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FFor the first time, the annual report
OL,12,Fincludes the Earth's energy imbalance.
OL,14,FThis measures the rate at which energy
OL,15,Ffrom the sun enters and then leaves
OL,16,Fits system.
OL,18,FUnder a stable climate, incoming
OL,19,Fenergy is about the same as the amount
OL,20,Fof outgoing energy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
