PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774314171
OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FHowever, scientists found that Earth's
OL,7,Fenergy imbalance reached a new high
OL,8,Flast year after increasing since
OL,9,Fobservational records began in 1960,
OL,10,Fparticularly in the past 20 years.
OL,12,FIt comes as concentrations of heat-
OL,13,Ftrapping greenhouse gases, carbon
OL,14,Fdioxide, methane, and nitrous oxide
OL,15,Fhave risen to their highest level in
OL,16,Fat least 800,000 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
