PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1774314171
OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FElsewhere, the report highlights the
OL,7,Fcascading impacts of extreme weather
OL,8,Fevents on communities worldwide,
OL,9,Fincluding food insecurity,
OL,10,Fdisplacement, and health risks driven
OL,11,Fby shifting rainfall patterns, such as
OL,12,Fthe mosquito-borne dengue and heat
OL,13,Fstress.
OL,15,FHowever, the report outlined how
OL,16,Fclimate data, early warning systems,
OL,17,Fand integrated climate services for
OL,18,Fhealth can protect people in a warming
OL,19,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
