OL,3,CGlobal climate is in a 'state of
OL,4,Cemergency', UN Secretary-General warns
OL,6,FThe report is based on scientific
OL,7,Fcontributions from National
OL,8,FMeteorological and Hydrological
OL,9,FServices, WMO Regional Climate
OL,10,FCentres, United Nations partners, and
OL,11,Fdozens of experts.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
